  "learn": {
    "title": "Funda",
    "coreCurriculumSubtitle": "Ikharikhulamu Eyisisekelo ye-P2P iwuhambo oluyisisekelo lokuba umfundi lweNethiwekhi Yomhlaba Wonke Yokufunda IBhayibheli ye-P2P — ithuthukiswe ngomthandazo ngaphansi kokuqondisa kukaMoya oNgcwele, futhi igxile ngokuqinile egunyeni lemiBhalo. Ikhona ukuze iqinise amakholwa kuKristu, iwaqondise ekuvuthweni komoya, futhi iphakamise abenzi babafundi abaphatha ithonya loMbuso kuyo yonke imikhakha yomphakathi.",
